<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>سُورَةُ الْكَوْثَرِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَنِ الرَّحِيمِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(فَصَلِّ لِرَبِّكَ وَانْحَرْ (٢)</span> إِنَّ شَانِئَكَ هُوَ الْأَبْتَرُ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>) .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(فَصَلِّ)</span> : الْفَاءُ لِلتَّعْقِيبِ؛ أَيْ عَقِبَ انْقِضَاءِ الصَّلَاةِ. وَ <span class="c2">(هُوَ)</span> : مُبْتَدَأٌ، أَوْ تَوْكِيدٌ، أَوْ فَصْلٌ. وَاللَّهُ أَعْلَمُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>